244
00:17:24,545 --> 00:17:26,673
Anda bisa kehilangan tiga mesin dan pulang.

245
00:17:26,673 --> 00:17:30,093
Anda bisa kehilangan setengahnya
penstabil vertikal Anda di bagian ekor

246
00:17:30,093 --> 00:17:31,219
